172
00:33:47,700 --> 00:33:50,600
Jadi, bagaimana denganmu, nak?

173
00:33:51,400 --> 00:33:56,700
Sepanjang hari, kau tak melakukan apa-apa selain
tidur-tiduran disini.

174
00:33:57,100 --> 00:33:59,800
Jika anak muda hidup seperti itu hari demi hari,

175
00:33:59,800 --> 00:34:01,500
